</span><span begin="52.540" end="53.160">言</span><span begin="53.210" end="53.510">葉</span><span begin="53.530" end="53.940">を</span><span begin="54.040" end="54.300">待</span><span begin="54.300" end="54.410">っ</span><span begin="54.410" end="54.550">て</span><span begin="54.580" end="54.770">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我在等待着你的话语</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata no kotoba o matteru</span></p><p begin="56.080" end="1:01.120" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.080" end="56.530">足</span><span begin="56.560" end="56.830">並</span><span begin="56.880" end="57.180">み</span><span begin="57.180" end="57.430">を</span><span begin="57.500" end="58.040">揃</span><span begin="58.040" end="58.310">え</span><span begin="58.340" end="58.520">ず</span><span begin="58.570" end="58.820">に</span><span begin="59.160" end="59.440">広</span><span begin="59.500" end="59.840">ま</span><span begin="59.870" end="1:00.050">る</span><span begin="1:00.050" end="1:00.490">歌</span><span begin="1:00.520" end="1:01.120">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">步伐不一地四处传唱的歌</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ashinami o soroezu ni hiromaru uta wa</span></p><p begin="1:01.490" end="1:06.760" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.490" end="1:01.830">本</span><span begin="1:01.860" end="1:02.400">当</span><span begin="1:02.520" end="1:02.750">の</span><span begin="1:03.200" end="1:03.820">私</span><span begin="1:03.820" end="1:03.880">じ</span><span begin="1:03.880" end="1:04.110">ゃ</span><span begin="1:04.540" end="1:04.690">な</span><span begin="1:04.690" end="1:04.800">い</span><span begin="1:04.860" end="1:05.080">か</span><span begin="1:05.200" end="1:05.400">も</span><span begin="1:05.480" end="1:05.830">し</span><span begin="1:05.890" end="1:06.480">れ</span><span begin="1:06.530" end="1:06.690">な</span><span begin="1:06.690" end="1:06.760">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">或许并不是真正的我</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hontou no watashi janai kamo shirenai</span></p><p begin="1:07.200" end="1:10.730" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.200" end="1:07.500">だ</span><span begin="1:07.560" end="1:07.830">け</span><span begin="1:07.880" end="1:08.100">ど</span><span begin="1:08.550" end="1:08.800">確</span><span begin="1:08.870" end="1:09.040">か</span><span begin="1:09.040" end="1:09.120">に</span><span begin="1:09.190" end="1:09.530">感</span><span begin="1:09.530" end="1:09.690">じ</span><span begin="1:09.720" end="1:09.820">る</span><span begin="1:09.860" end="1:09.980">も</span><span begin="1:10.010" end="1:10.150">の</span><span begin="1:10.180" end="1:10.360">が</span><span begin="1:10.360" end="1:10.550">あ</span><span begin="1:10.550" end="1:10.730">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但的确有着能真切感受到的东西</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakedo tashika ni kanjiru mono ga aru</span></p><p begin="1:24.040" end="1:26.830" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.040" end="1:24.140">自</span><span begin="1:24.190" end="1:24.530">信</span><span begin="1:24.530" end="1:24.650">が</span><span begin="1:24.650" end="1:24.850">揺</span><span begin="1:24.880" end="1:25.000">れ</span><span begin="1:25.020" end="1:25.140">る</span><span begin="1:25.200" end="1:25.470">時</span><span begin="1:25.530" end="1:25.800">も</span><span begin="1:25.880" end="1:26.190">あ</span><span begin="1:26.220" end="1:26.350">る</span><span begin="1:26.350" end="1:26.560">ん</span><span begin="1:26.560" end="1:26.830">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也有自信动摇的时候啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jishin ga yureru toki mo arunda</span></p><p begin="1:29.370" end="1:32.140" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.370" end="1:29.830">私</span><span begin="1:29.880" end="1:30.010">の</span><span begin="1:30.010" end="1:30.130">良</span><span begin="1:30.180" end="1:30.370">さ</span><span begin="1:30.370" end="1:30.530">っ</span><span begin="1:30.530" end="1:30.760">て</span><span begin="1:30.860" end="1:31.320">な</span><span begin="1:31.320" end="1:31.540">ん</span><span begin="1:31.540" end="1:31.710">だ</span><span begin="1:31.710" end="1:32.060">ろ</span><span begin="1:32.060" end="1:32.140">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的优点究竟是什么呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi no yosa tte nandarou</span></p><p begin="1:33.490" end="1:38.850" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.490" end="1:33.660">そ</span><span begin="1:33.660" end="1:33.830">う</span><span begin="1:33.830" end="1:34.460">思</span><span begin="1:34.550" end="1:34.830">い</span><span begin="1:35.210" end="1:35.750">悩</span><span begin="1:35.860" end="1:36.110">む</span><span begin="1:36.540" end="1:37.160">時</span><span begin="1:37.200" end="1:37.450">に</span><span begin="1:37.530" end="1:37.730">は</span><span begin="1:37.900" end="1:38.530">も</span><span begin="1:38.530" end="1:38.850">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我这样烦恼的时候却已经</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sou omoinayamu toki ni wa mou</span></p><p begin="1:39.160" end="1:42.730" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:39.160" end="1:39.520">す</span><span begin="1:39.550" end="1:39.830">で</span><span begin="1:39.870" end="1:40.060">に</span><span begin="1:40.550" end="1:40.820">誰</span><span begin="1:40.870" end="1:41.000">か</span><span begin="1:41.020" end="1:41.130">の</span><span begin="1:41.180" end="1:41.470">生</span><span begin="1:41.530" end="1:41.820">活</span><span begin="1:41.870" end="1:42.120">の</span><span begin="1:42.220" end="1:42.510">一</span><span begin="1:42.550" end="1:42.730">部</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">成为了某个人生活的一部分</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sudeni dareka no seikatsu no ichibu</span></p><p begin="1:43.830" end="1:48.850" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:43.830" end="1:44.120">好</span><span begin="1:44.190" end="1:44.450">き</span><span begin="1:44.520" end="1:44.750">な</span><span begin="1:45.190" end="1:45.810">歌</span><span begin="1:45.840" end="1:46.120">を</span><span begin="1:46.480" end="1:46.610">好</span><span begin="1:46.670" end="1:46.800">き</span><span begin="1:46.840" end="1:47.100">な</span><span begin="1:47.170" end="1:47.510">よ</span><span begin="1:47.510" end="1:47.810">う</span><span begin="1:47.880" end="1:48.160">に</span><span begin="1:48.160" end="1:48.550">歌</span><span begin="1:48.550" end="1:48.850">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">按自己喜欢的方式唱着喜欢的歌</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Suki na uta o suki na you ni utau</span></p><p begin="1:49.170" end="1:53.460" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.170" end="1:49.510">そ</span><span begin="1:49.530" end="1:49.680">れ</span><span begin="1:49.690" end="1:49.820">だ</span><span begin="1:49.890" end="1:50.150">け</span><span begin="1:50.180" end="1:50.570">は</span><span begin="1:51.200" end="1:51.480">何</span><span begin="1:51.560" end="1:51.740">も</span><span begin="1:52.170" end="1:52.450">変</span><span begin="1:52.480" end="1:52.820">わ</span><span begin="1:52.840" end="1:52.990">ら</span><span begin="1:53.010" end="1:53.220">な</span><span begin="1:53.220" end="1:53.460">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">唯有这一点不会有任何改变</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore dake wa nani mo kawaranai</span></p><p begin="1:53.860" end="1:57.730" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.860" end="1:54.010">で</span><span begin="1:54.070" end="1:54.520">も</span><span begin="1:54.520" end="1:55.190">忘</span><span begin="1:55.210" end="1:55.310">れ</span><span begin="1:55.370" end="1:55.880">去</span><span begin="1:55.880" end="1:56.040">ら</span><span begin="1:56.060" end="1:56.460">れ</span><span begin="1:56.530" end="1:56.690">て</span><span begin="1:56.720" end="1:56.800">し</span><span begin="1:56.840" end="1:57.240">ま</span><span begin="1:57.240" end="1:57.320">う</span><span begin="1:57.340" end="1:57.470">の</span><span begin="1:57.520" end="1:57.730">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但我会被彻底遗忘吗</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Demo wasuresararete shimau no ka</span></p><p begin="1:57.860" end="1:59.410" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.860" end="1:58.470">時</span><span begin="1:58.520" end="1:58.800">が</span><span begin="1:58.880" end="1:58.970">経</span><span begin="1:59.040" end="1:59.160">て</span><span begin="1:59.230" end="1:59.410">ば</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">随着时间流逝的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Toki ga tateba</span></p><p begin="2:00.180" end="2:01.390" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.180" end="2:00.620">まあ</span><span begin="2:00.850" end="2:01.030">い</span><span begin="2:01.030" end="2:01.210">い</span><span begin="2:01.210" end="2:01.390">や</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">算了不管了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Maa ii ya</span></p><p begin="2:01.840" end="2:04.080" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:01.840" end="2:02.170">今</span><span begin="2:02.200" end="2:02.420">は</span><span begin="2:02.550" end="2:03.070">楽</span><span begin="2:03.160" end="2:03.440">し</span><span begin="2:03.440" end="2:03.630">い</span><span begin="2:03.710" end="2:03.880">か</span><span begin="2:03.890" end="2:04.080">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为现在很开心</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima wa tanoshii kara</span></p><p begin="2:05.340" end="2:10.450" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:05.340" end="2:05.710">波</span><span begin="2:05.710" end="2:05.810">打</span><span begin="2:05.880" end="2:05.980">つ</span><span begin="2:06.020" end="2:07.100">心</span><span begin="2:07.170" end="2:07.290">の</span><span begin="2:07.340" end="2:07.650">細</span><span begin="2:07.690" end="2:07.880">部</span><span begin="2:07.880" end="2:08.190">は</span><span begin="2:08.520" end="2:08.640">あ</span><span begin="2:08.680" end="2:08.780">な</span><span begin="2:08.840" end="2:09.150">た</span><span begin="2:09.180" end="2:09.320">の</span><span begin="2:09.390" end="2:09.860">声</span><span begin="2:09.890" end="2:10.450">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">泛起波澜的内心的细微之处全都是你的声音</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namiutsu kokoro no saibu wa anata no koe de</span></p><p begin="2:11.160" end="2:14.710" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:11.160" end="2:12.020">私</span><span begin="2:12.040" end="2:12.380">は</span><span begin="2:12.550" end="2:13.050">今</span><span begin="2:13.510" end="2:13.790">こ</span><span begin="2:13.860" end="2:14.140">こ</span><span begin="2:14.220" end="2:14.380">に</span><span begin="2:14.380" end="2:14.530">い</span><span begin="2:14.550" end="2:14.710">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我现在就在这里</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi wa ima koko ni iru</span></p><p begin="2:16.190" end="2:18.850" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:16.190" end="2:16.380">も</span><span begin="2:16.380" end="2:16.490">う</span><span begin="2:16.540" end="2:17.150">何</span><span begin="2:17.210" end="2:17.460">も</span><span begin="2:17.540" end="2:17.830">気</span><span begin="2:17.850" end="2:17.960">に</span><span begin="2:18.040" end="2:18.340">し</span><span begin="2:18.360" end="2:18.570">な</span><span begin="2:18.570" end="2:18.850">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">已经什么都不在意了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mou nani mo ki ni shinai</span></p><p begin="2:19.170" end="2:26.740" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:19.170" end="2:19.510">そ</span><span begin="2:19.510" end="2:19.830">う</span><span begin="2:19.830" end="2:20.030">言</span><span begin="2:20.030" end="2:20.240">え</span><span begin="2:20.240" end="2:20.340">る</span><span begin="2:20.360" end="2:20.500">の</span><span begin="2:20.520" end="2:21.080">は</span><span begin="2:21.520" end="2:21.860">単</span><span begin="2:21.860" end="2:22.530">純</span><span begin="2:22.530" end="2:22.710">な</span><span begin="2:23.170" end="2:23.390">思</span><span begin="2:23.530" end="2:24.040">考</span><span begin="2:24.520" end="2:25.200">回</span><span begin="2:25.200" end="2:25.500">路</span><span begin="2:25.540" end="2:25.680">だ</span><span begin="2:25.860" end="2:26.510">か</span><span begin="2:26.540" end="2:26.740">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">能够这样说是因为思考回路很简单吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sou ieru no wa tanjun na shikoukairo dakara</span></p><p begin="2:27.130" end="2:30.770" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:27.130" end="2:27.500">そ</span><span begin="2:27.520" end="2:27.670">れ</span><span begin="2:27.700" end="2:27.830">で</span><span begin="2:27.870" end="2:28.080">も</span><span begin="2:28.550" end="2:28.800">大</span><span begin="2:28.850" end="2:29.150">切</span><span begin="2:29.200" end="2:29.430">な</span><span begin="2:29.520" end="2:29.780">も</span><span begin="2:29.860" end="2:30.120">の</span><span begin="2:30.190" end="2:30.380">が</span><span begin="2:30.380" end="2:30.540">あ</span><span begin="2:30.570" end="2:30.770">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使如此也有珍视的事物</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo taisetsu na mono ga aru</span></p><p begin="2:35.170" end="2:38.840" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:35.170" end="2:35.600">並</span><span begin="2:35.680" end="2:35.790">木</span><span begin="2:35.840" end="2:36.170">道</span><span begin="2:36.190" end="2:36.450">を</span><span begin="2:36.520" end="2:36.610">聞</span><span begin="2:36.680" end="2:36.780">き</span><span begin="2:36.850" end="2:37.020">込</span><span begin="2:37.020" end="2:37.180">ん</span><span begin="2:37.180" end="2:37.370">だ</span><span begin="2:37.370" end="2:37.720">歌</span><span begin="2:37.870" end="2:38.180">で</span><span begin="2:38.180" end="2:38.530">歩</span><span begin="2:38.590" end="2:38.840">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伴着听熟的歌走在林荫道上</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namikimichi o kikikonda uta de aruku</span></p><p begin="2:40.500" end="2:44.700" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:40.500" end="2:40.610">ま</span><span begin="2:40.690" end="2:40.830">た</span><span begin="2:40.860" end="2:41.010">ね</span><span begin="2:41.010" end="2:41.190">っ</span><span begin="2:41.190" end="2:41.530">て</span><span begin="2:41.530" end="2:41.690">言</span><span begin="2:41.690" end="2:41.860">い</span><span begin="2:41.870" end="2:42.060">合</span><span begin="2:42.060" end="2:42.190">っ</span><span begin="2:42.190" end="2:42.400">た</span><span begin="2:42.850" end="2:43.500">帰</span><span begin="2:43.540" end="2:43.960">り</span><span begin="2:44.040" end="2:44.700">路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">互道着明天见的回家路上</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mata ne tte iiatta kaerimichi</span></p><p begin="2:45.830" end="2:50.760" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.830" end="2:46.140">変</span><span begin="2:46.180" end="2:46.510">わ</span><span begin="2:46.540" end="2:46.800">る</span><span begin="2:47.160" end="2:47.370">も</span><span begin="2:47.550" end="2:47.790">の</span><span begin="2:47.870" end="2:48.130">と</span><span begin="2:48.510" end="2:48.650">変</span><span begin="2:48.680" end="2:48.860">わ</span><span begin="2:48.890" end="2:49.090">ら</span><span begin="2:49.200" end="2:49.480">な</span><span begin="2:49.540" end="2:49.780">い</span><span begin="2:49.880" end="2:50.470">も</span><span begin="2:50.520" end="2:50.760">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">会改变的事物与不会改变的事物</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kawaru mono to kawaranai mono</span></p><p begin="2:51.200" end="2:56.140" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:51.200" end="2:52.200">青</span><span begin="2:52.200" end="2:52.340">い</span><span begin="2:52.380" end="2:52.520">目</span><span begin="2:52.590" end="2:52.780">と</span><span begin="2:53.190" end="2:53.790">桜</span><span begin="2:53.900" end="2:54.140">色</span><span begin="2:54.220" end="2:54.400">に</span><span begin="2:54.880" end="2:55.130">な</span><span begin="2:55.200" end="2:55.440">び</span><span begin="2:55.540" end="2:55.640">く</span><span begin="2:55.710" end="2:56.140">髪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">蓝色的眼眸与随风飘动的樱色长发</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aoi me to sakurairo ni nabiku kami</span></p><p begin="2:56.510" end="3:00.160" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:56.510" end="2:57.190">私</span><span begin="2:57.230" end="2:57.480">は</span><span begin="2:57.900" end="2:58.210">ど</span><span begin="2:58.240" end="2:58.450">う</span><span begin="2:58.900" end="2:59.180">見</span><span begin="2:59.210" end="2:59.510">え</span><span begin="2:59.540" end="2:59.640">る</span><span begin="2:59.720" end="2:59.870">か</span><span begin="2:59.920" end="3:00.160">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在你眼中我看起来是怎样的呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi wa dou mieru kana</span></p><p begin="3:04.040" end="3:09.180" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:04.040" end="3:04.280">楽</span><span begin="3:04.330" end="3:04.450">し</span><span begin="3:04.520" end="3:04.710">く</span><span begin="3:04.710" end="3:04.850">っ</span><span begin="3:04.850" end="3:05.410">て</span><span begin="3:05.480" end="3:05.780">仕</span><span begin="3:05.830" end="3:06.310">方</span><span begin="3:06.350" end="3:06.570">な</span><span begin="3:06.570" end="3:06.790">い</span><span begin="3:07.190" end="3:07.400">こ</span><span begin="3:07.510" end="3:07.810">の</span><span begin="3:07.870" end="3:08.020">景</span><span begin="3:08.060" end="3:08.520">色</span><span begin="3:08.550" end="3:09.180">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将这开心得无以复加的景色</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tanoshikutte shikatanai kono keshiki o</span></p><p begin="3:09.860" end="3:13.470" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:09.860" end="3:10.190">振</span><span begin="3:10.190" end="3:10.460">り</span><span begin="3:10.530" end="3:11.160">返</span><span begin="3:11.210" end="3:11.440">る</span><span begin="3:11.480" end="3:12.060">暇</span><span begin="3:12.200" end="3:12.800">も</span><span begin="3:12.860" end="3:13.110">な</span><span begin="3:13.200" end="3:13.470">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">连回味的闲暇都没有</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Furikaeru hima mo naku</span></p><p begin="3:14.820" end="3:19.740" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:14.820" end="3:15.230">早</span><span begin="3:15.230" end="3:15.830">足</span><span begin="3:15.870" end="3:16.140">で</span><span begin="3:16.200" end="3:16.460">駆</span><span begin="3:16.520" end="3:16.670">け</span><span begin="3:16.690" end="3:17.030">る</span><span begin="3:17.030" end="3:17.160">よ</span><span begin="3:17.160" end="3:17.210">う</span><span begin="3:17.210" end="3:17.480">に</span><span begin="3:17.850" end="3:18.120">広</span><span begin="3:18.170" end="3:18.520">ま</span><span begin="3:18.550" end="3:18.710">る</span><span begin="3:18.710" end="3:19.160">歌</span><span begin="3:19.180" end="3:19.740">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仿佛快步奔跑般四处传唱的歌</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hayaashi de kakeru you ni hiromaru uta wa</span></p><p begin="3:20.150" end="3:25.460" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:20.150" end="3:20.470">本</span><span begin="3:20.510" end="3:21.070">当</span><span begin="3:21.210" end="3:21.480">の</span><span begin="3:21.860" end="3:22.460">私</span><span begin="3:22.480" end="3:22.550">じ</span><span begin="3:22.550" end="3:22.810">ゃ</span><span begin="3:23.190" end="3:23.330">な</span><span begin="3:23.330" end="3:23.470">い</span><span begin="3:23.520" end="3:23.750">か</span><span begin="3:23.870" end="3:24.080">も</span><span begin="3:24.150" end="3:24.450">し</span><span begin="3:24.530" end="3:25.180">れ</span><span begin="3:25.220" end="3:25.390">な</span><span begin="3:25.390" end="3:25.460">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">或许并不是真正的我</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hontou no watashi janai kamo shirenai</span></p><p begin="3:25.820" end="3:29.440" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:25.820" end="3:26.190">そ</span><span begin="3:26.190" end="3:26.340">れ</span><span begin="3:26.360" end="3:26.490">で</span><span begin="3:26.540" end="3:26.750">も</span><span begin="3:27.190" end="3:27.470">確</span><span begin="3:27.530" end="3:27.830">か</span><span begin="3:27.880" end="3:28.100">に</span><span begin="3:28.160" end="3:28.800">信</span><span begin="3:28.830" end="3:28.990">じ</span><span begin="3:29.050" end="3:29.210">て</span><span begin="3:29.230" end="3:29.440">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使如此我也真切地相信着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo tashika ni shinjiteru</span></p><p begin="3:30.820" end="3:34.780" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.820" end="3:31.110">ワ</span><span begin="3:31.180" end="3:31.460">ク</span><span begin="3:31.490" end="3:31.660">ワ</span><span begin="3:31.710" end="3:31.850">ク</span><span begin="3:31.880" end="3:32.090">で</span><span begin="3:32.520" end="3:32.640">止</span><span begin="3:32.710" end="3:32.840">ま</span><span begin="3:32.860" end="3:33.010">ら</span><span begin="3:33.050" end="3:33.160">な</span><span begin="3:33.210" end="3:33.440">い</span><span begin="3:33.560" end="3:33.840">に</span><span begin="3:33.840" end="3:34.170">や</span><span begin="3:34.230" end="3:34.370">に</span><span begin="3:34.370" end="3:34.490">や</span><span begin="3:34.580" end="3:34.780">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">兴奋不已停不住的傻笑也是</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Wakuwaku de tomaranai niyaniya mo</span></p><p begin="3:36.160" end="3:40.110" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:36.160" end="3:36.790">本</span><span begin="3:36.840" end="3:37.170">当</span><span begin="3:37.220" end="3:37.440">の</span><span begin="3:37.850" end="3:37.950">あ</span><span begin="3:38.030" end="3:38.150">な</span><span begin="3:38.210" end="3:38.500">た</span><span begin="3:38.540" end="3:38.790">の</span><span begin="3:38.880" end="3:39.460">観</span><span begin="3:39.520" end="3:39.780">測</span><span begin="3:39.880" end="3:40.110">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">真正的你的观测也是</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hontou no anata no kansoku mo</span></p></div></body></tt>